---

# Todolist Manager

Manage tasks in Feishu Bitable. Automatically capture ideas, log progress, and perform daily reviews.

## Critical Rules

- Never delete task records - Only create and update
- Status control - AI can only set "待启动(AI提交)" and "待验收(AI提交)"
- Append logs - Never overwrite existing logs
- Log as cache - Task logs serve as temporary cache for daily review

---

## Dynamic Todolist Discovery

规范：所有todolist 多维表的描述必须包含 "todolist" 关键词。

技能启动时自动扫描所有符合规范的多维表，根据描述内容智能路由到正确的表。

### Standard Field Reference

| Logical Name | Common Names | Type | AI Permission | Notes |
|--------------|--------------|------|---------------|-------|
| title | 任务名称, 工作目标, 事项名称 | Text(1) | Create | Required |
| description | 任务描述, 目标说明, 描述 | Text(1) | Create | Can include sub-items |
| status | 任务状态, 完成状态, 状态 | SingleSelect(3) | Limited | Only AI-specific statuses |
| log | 任务日志, 进展记录, 日志 | Text(1) | Append | Progress cache, append only |
| log_date | 日志最后更新日期 | DateTime(5) | Update | Millisecond timestamp |
| dispatch_date | 派发日期 | DateTime(5) | Create | Millisecond timestamp |
| deadline | 截止日期 | DateTime(5) | User only | - |
| owner | 任务执行者 | User(11) | User only | Format: `[{id:"ou_xxx"}]` |
| priority | 任务优先级, 优先级 | SingleSelect(3) | Create only | 1/2/3/9/0/其他 |
| module | 所属模块, 分类 | SingleSelect(3) | Create only | Optional |
| risk | 风险总结 | Text(1) | Update | Risk description |

**AI-Settable Statuses:**
- `待启动(AI提交)` - AI-captured idea, awaiting user review
- `待验收(AI提交)` - AI judges complete, awaiting user verification

---

## Core Functions

### Load All Todolists

```javascript
async function loadAllTodolists() {
  const apps = await feishu_bitable_app({ action: "list", page_size: 100 })
  
  return apps.items
    .filter(app => app.description && app.description.includes('todolist'))
    .map(app => ({
      app_token: app.app_token,
      name: app.name,
      description: app.description
    }))
}
```

### Route to Target List

```javascript
async function routeToList(userInput, todolists) {
  if (todolists.length === 1) return todolists[0]
  
  // LLM 判断
  const prompt = `用户说：${userInput}

现有 todolist:\n${todolists.map((l, i) => `${i+1}. ${l.name}: ${l.description}`).join('\n')}

返回最合适的序号(1-${todolists.length})，不确定时返回1。只返回数字。`
  
  // 推理得到选择
  const choice = 1  // 默认第一个
  return todolists[choice - 1]
}
```

### Resolve Field Name

```javascript
const FIELD_CANDIDATES = {
  title: ["任务名称", "工作目标", "事项名称", "标题"],
  description: ["任务描述", "目标说明", "描述", "详情"],
  status: ["任务状态", "完成状态", "状态"],
  log: ["任务日志", "进展记录", "日志", "备注"],
  log_date: ["日志最后更新日期"],
  dispatch_date: ["派发日期"],
  priority: ["任务优先级", "优先级"],
  module: ["所属模块", "分类", "模块"]
}

function resolveFieldName(tableFields, logicalName) {
  const candidates = FIELD_CANDIDATES[logicalName]
  for (const name of candidates) {
    if (tableFields.some(f => f.field_name === name)) return name
  }
  return null
}
```

