### Scenario 4: Create New Todolist

**Trigger:** User explicitly says "创建/新建 todolist"

**Process:**

```javascript
// 1. Create App
const app = await feishu_bitable_app({ action: "create", name: listName })

// 2. Update description (must include "todolist")
await feishu_bitable_app({
  action: "patch",
  app_token: app.app_token,
  name: listName,
  description: `todolist: ${purpose}`
})

// 3. Create table with standard fields
const STANDARD_FIELDS = [
  { field_name: "任务名称", type: 1 },
  { field_name: "任务描述", type: 1 },
  { field_name: "任务状态", type: 3, property: {
    options: [
      { name: "待启动(AI提交)" },
      { name: "未启动" },
      { name: "进行中" },
      { name: "待验收(AI提交)" },
      { name: "已完成" },
      { name: "取消" }
    ]
  }},
  { field_name: "任务日志", type: 1 },
  { field_name: "日志最后更新日期", type: 5 },
  { field_name: "派发日期", type: 5 },
  { field_name: "截止日期", type: 5 },
  { field_name: "任务优先级", type: 3, property: { options: [{ name: "1" }, { name: "2" }, { name: "3" }] }},
  { field_name: "风险总结", type: 1 }
]

await feishu_bitable_app_table({
  action: "create",
  app_token: app.app_token,
  table: { name: "待办事项", fields: STANDARD_FIELDS }
})
```

---

## Common Questions

**Q: How to identify which task is being discussed?**
A: Match task name keywords, understand from context, or ask user.

**Q: How to avoid overwriting logs?**
A: Always read existing log first, then append with `\n\n`.

**Q: Why can't AI delete tasks?**
A: Deletion causes information loss. Instead, set status to "取消" and log reason.

**Q: Which fields can AI modify?**
- Can modify: 任务日志, 日志最后更新日期, 风险总结
- Conditional: 任务状态 (only to AI-specific statuses)
- Cannot modify: 任务执行者, 截止日期, 任务优先级

---

## Integration Notes

### Daily Review Trigger

Configure in `~/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md`:
```markdown
## Todolist Daily Review
Check once daily (evening recommended):
Invoke todolist-manager skill Scenario 3
```

Or use cron:
```bash
openclaw cron add \
  --name "Todolist review" \
  --cron "0 22 * * *" \
  --session isolated \
  --message "Execute todolist daily review"
```

### Field Type Reference

| type | ui_type | Format |
|------|---------|--------|
| 1 | Text | String |
| 3 | SingleSelect | String (option name) |
| 5 | DateTime | Millisecond timestamp |
| 11 | User | `[{id:"ou_xxx"}]` |

